line_1: Tongues, arts, and arms, and history,
line_2: And in the endless labour die.
As if the Ancient Paths they could discry,

line_1: And Fame grow Proud to Print their History.
line_2: The World shall blush, when they their Picture see,

line_1: And trace the Scots in Modern History:
line_2: Should we to recent Memory apply,
And many a copious narrative you'll see,
